source.name: Bronx Facilities
source.description: The location, type and capacity of public and private community facilities in New York City, including schools, parks, libraries, public safety, day care, foster care, special needs housing, health and mental health facilities and programs. Refer to SelFac_datainfo.pdf for facility type designation and definition.
